english:
Breast {ARMOR}
Don't sweat it.
You had no choice back then.
...It wasn't your fault, {WARRICK}.\pBREAST {ARMOR}
Truth is, I was relieved to be sold.

Brest {ARMOR}
Heh.
You've grown strong, {WARRICK}.
But me... I'm just as I was.\pBREST {ARMOR}
You've become so strong.
You've grown so much.
{...}..And I haven't changed at all.\pBREST {ARMOR}
Forgive me, {WARRICK}.
I haven't changed one bit.
I can't lend you any of my strength.

Brest {ARMOR}
{...}..Heh.
I'm happy, {WARRICK}.
To hear that from a man who'll
be a {GUARDIAN}.\pBREST {ARMOR}
I'm the happiest armor
in all the world.\pBREST {ARMOR}
...Give it your all, {WARRICK}.
We'll be... with you...
always..{...}..{...}.

{STEINER}, the Black {GUARDIAN}
Knight.
What is he thinking, siding with
the {DEMON GOD}{...}

Whoa!?
There's a letter tucked in the chest.
Shall I read it?\p{FURNIS}
...Let's see now.
'A kind gift from {MARGIS}.'\p{FURNIS}
...What is this?
